name: Peter Joosten
note:
Results:
Company Name: R&B Veiligheid BV

Company Website: https://www.safety-consultants.eu/

Contact Person: Peter Joosten

Product: R&B Safety Consultants is therefore providing safety courses such as VCA and BHV, on location at a client or in one of our classrooms. Because safety must be part of the corporate culture and the mentality of every employee. Regular training is a prerequisite for this.

R&B Safety BV has all the know-how for a correct and flexible safety policy. That is why we do everything we can to keep up with the latest developments in order to provide optimal added value for our customers and to be able to act in such a way: A point of contact for all your security questions.
Flexible and smooth customer service.
Continuous training and coaching of employees.

Country-Location:  Netherlands

Target Audience: worldwide

Immediate Requirement: PR manager, lead generation manager.

Next contact day: we are going to have the 2nd call on Wednesday, 16 pm our time to discuss everything in details. I will invite one candidate from each department. Clients want to hear ideas from our side how we can help their business.
